title: Cosmic Queries: The Space Race
description: What did politics and the Cold War have to do with the space race? On the flip side, how did the Apollo program and landing on the Moon impact us here on Earth? Neil deGrasse Tyson answers fan-submitted questions chosen by co-host Chuck Nice.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
